{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":984,"text":"So, my mother's a pediatrician,"},{"time":3972,"text":"and when I was young,\nshe'd tell the craziest stories"},{"time":7810,"text":"that combined science\nwith her overactive imagination."},{"time":11624,"text":"One of the stories she told\nwas that if you eat a lot of salt,"},{"time":15799,"text":"all of the blood rushes up your legs,"},{"time":19492,"text":"through your body,"},{"time":20768,"text":"and shoots out the top of your head,"},{"time":22871,"text":"killing you instantly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24597,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":25681,"text":"She called it \"high blood pressure.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":27517,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":29185,"text":"This was my first experience\nwith science fiction,"},{"time":32119,"text":"and I loved it."},{"time":33951,"text":"So when I started to write\nmy own science fiction and fantasy,"},{"time":37102,"text":"I was surprised that it\nwas considered un-African."},{"time":40294,"text":"So naturally, I asked, what is African?"},{"time":42933,"text":"And this is what I know so far:"},{"time":45735,"text":"Africa is important."},{"time":48023,"text":"Africa is the future."},{"time":49478,"text":"It is, though."},{"time":51254,"text":"And Africa is a serious place\nwhere only serious things happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55601,"text":"So when I present my work somewhere,\nsomeone will always ask,"},{"time":60100,"text":"\"What's so important about it?"},{"time":62695,"text":"How does it deal with real African issues"},{"time":65238,"text":"like war, poverty, devastation or AIDS?\""},{"time":70630,"text":"And it doesn't."},{"time":72287,"text":"My work is about Nairobi pop bands\nthat want to go to space"},{"time":77648,"text":"or about seven-foot-tall robots"},{"time":80800,"text":"that fall in love."},{"time":82673,"text":"It's nothing incredibly important."},{"time":85910,"text":"It's just fun, fierce and frivolous,"},{"time":89317,"text":"as frivolous as bubble gum --"},{"time":91952,"text":"\"AfroBubbleGum.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":94421,"text":"So I'm not saying that\nagenda art isn't important;"},{"time":97710,"text":"I'm the chairperson of a charity"},{"time":100009,"text":"that deals with films and theaters\nthat write about HIV and radicalization"},{"time":106990,"text":"and female genital mutilation."},{"time":109277,"text":"It's vital and important art,"},{"time":111582,"text":"but it cannot be the only art\nthat comes out of the continent."},{"time":116372,"text":"We have to tell more stories"},{"time":118732,"text":"that are vibrant."},{"time":121277,"text":"The danger of the single story\nis still being realized."},{"time":126059,"text":"And maybe it's because of the funding."},{"time":127902,"text":"A lot of art is still dependent\non developmental aid."},{"time":131829,"text":"So art becomes a tool for agenda."},{"time":135910,"text":"Or maybe it's because we've only seen\none image of ourselves for so long"},{"time":140352,"text":"that that's all we know how to create."},{"time":142823,"text":"Whatever the reason, we need a new way,"},{"time":146020,"text":"and AfroBubbleGum is one approach."},{"time":148571,"text":"It's the advocacy of art for art's sake."},{"time":152669,"text":"It's the advocacy of art\nthat is not policy-driven"},{"time":155689,"text":"or agenda-driven"},{"time":157245,"text":"or based on education,"},{"time":159208,"text":"just for the sake of imagination:"},{"time":162598,"text":"AfroBubbleGum art."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164829,"text":"And we can't all be AfroBubbleGumists."},{"time":167239,"text":"We have to judge our work\nfor its potential poverty porn pitfalls."},{"time":171309,"text":"We have to have tests\nthat are similar to the Bechdel test,"},{"time":177364,"text":"and ask questions like:"},{"time":179655,"text":"Are two or more Africans\nin this piece of fiction healthy?"},{"time":185096,"text":"Are those same Africans financially stable\nand not in need of saving?"},{"time":191373,"text":"Are they having fun and enjoying life?"},{"time":194285,"text":"And if we can answer yes\nto two or more of these questions,"},{"time":197407,"text":"then surely we're AfroBubbleGumists."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200035,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":201608,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":206409,"text":"And fun is political,"},{"time":208447,"text":"because imagine if we have\nimages of Africans who were vibrant"},{"time":212723,"text":"and loving and thriving"},{"time":214790,"text":"and living a beautiful, vibrant life."},{"time":217102,"text":"What would we think of ourselves then?"},{"time":219507,"text":"Would we think that maybe\nwe're worthy of more happiness?"},{"time":222979,"text":"Would we think of our shared humanity\nthrough our shared joy?"},{"time":227567,"text":"I think of these things when I create."},{"time":229947,"text":"I think of the people and the places\nthat give me immeasurable joy,"},{"time":233172,"text":"and I work to represent them."},{"time":235179,"text":"And that's why I write stories"},{"time":236840,"text":"about futuristic girls that risk\neverything to save plants"},{"time":241334,"text":"or to race camels"},{"time":243587,"text":"or even just to dance,"},{"time":246051,"text":"to honor fun,"},{"time":247796,"text":"because my world is mostly happy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249943,"text":"And I know happiness is a privilege\nin this current splintered world"},{"time":253737,"text":"where remaining hopeful\nrequires diligence."},{"time":259285,"text":"But maybe, if you join me\nin creating, curating and commissioning"},{"time":264652,"text":"more AfroBubbleGum art,"},{"time":266705,"text":"there might be hope\nfor a different view of the world,"},{"time":269507,"text":"a happy Africa view"},{"time":271687,"text":"where children are strangely traumatized"},{"time":273739,"text":"by their mother's dark sense of humor,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":275706,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":276767,"text":"but also they're claiming fun,\nfierce and frivolous art"},{"time":281353,"text":"in the name of all things\nunseriously African."},{"time":286090,"text":"Because we're AfroBubbleGumists"},{"time":288736,"text":"and there's so many more of us\nthan you can imagine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292090,"text":"Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":293318,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}